==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unburden
<hw>Un*bur"den</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>burden</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To relieve
from a burden.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To throw off, as a burden; to unload.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unburiable</ent>⟦br⟧
